Class HistoryBasedDirtyStateProvider

java.lang.Object
org.eclipse.gef.mvc.fx.ui.parts.HistoryBasedDirtyStateProvider
All Implemented Interfaces:
IDirtyStateProvider, IDisposable
public class HistoryBasedDirtyStateProvider extends Object implements IDirtyStateProvider, IDisposable
A support class to handle the dirty state of a WorkbenchPart that uses an IOperationHistory and an IUndoContext.
